        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1198140730" class="vote-count">13</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1198140730" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1198140730">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/145277079/">夏至</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar10 rating" title="很差"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-03</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">如果说第一部惊喜，第二部失望的话，那么第三部可以说完全是辣鸡🐔 了。充满了左派偏见以及作者可笑而肤浅的史观，还敢自称历史小说，麻烦作者吃口屎冷静一下。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1184655630">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1184655630" class="vote-count">18</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1184655630" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1184655630">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/141928471/">帅师桑</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-01</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">相比颠峰的第二部，这一部时间跨度太大，人物太多，性格塑造的不够饱满。前段和中段还是可圈可点的，后面几节的描写有些浮浅。看到年老体弱的菲茨捧着妹妹的照片说“Good days never come back”我的眼泪都掉下来了。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1187757051">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1187757051" class="vote-count">49</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1187757051" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1187757051">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/churunmeru/">CHANTEY</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">记叙了人类整整一百年历史的「世纪三部曲」，注定将留在我们这个时代的共同阅读记忆中。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1197479157">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1197479157" class="vote-count">6</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1197479157" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1197479157">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fengj1007/">大头</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">第三部不好，远不如前两部，人物性格一根筋，只有两件事情做:谈论政治和性，然后莫名其妙的见证了历史事件。作者对于历史倾向性也比较明显</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

