                <p>《永恒的边缘》随书附赠的大海报</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p43738950-1.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">《永恒的边缘》历史大事件</div></div></div><p></p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







